snippet.title: Subnautica available now through Xbox Game Preview
snippet.description: Now available through Xbox Game Preview! Subnautica is an underwater open world adventure game. Craft equipment, pilot submarines, and out-smart wildlife to explore lush coral reefs, volcanoes, and cave systems.
